    <item>
      <title>Verizon为在紧张市场中吸引订户提供新的特权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/verizon-offers-new-perks-to-woo-subscribers-in-tight-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Verizon Communications Inc.有望提供三年的价格保证和免费的电话交易，作为其最新产品的一部分，旨在吸引新客户并将现有客户保持在竞争激烈的无线市场中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/verizon-offers-new-perks-to-woo-subscribers-in-tight-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰克·多尔西（Jack Dorsey）的街区随着股票价格跌落而推向银行业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/jack-dorsey-s-block-pushes-into-banking-as-stock-price-tumbles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Cai Haun已成为忠实的现金应用程序用户已有近十年了。首先，使用Block Inc.的应用程序作为松鼠的咖啡师提示，现在是咖啡师的工作，现在可以从朋友那里寄钱喝酒和小组晚餐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/jack-dorsey-s-block-pushes-into-banking-as-stock-price-tumbles</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Tiktok面临的欧盟数据将罚款超过5亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/tiktok-faces-fine-over-500-million-for-eu-data-sent-to-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Tiktok所有者Bytedance Ltd.将被非法将欧洲用户的数据运送到中国的隐私罚款超过5亿欧元（5.53亿美元）的隐私罚款，从而增加了对视频共享应用程序的全球强烈反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/tiktok-faces-fine-over-500-million-for-eu-data-sent-to-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 11:37:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的总督支出斧头正在悬挂在技术库存上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/musk-s-doge-spending-axe-is-hanging-over-technology-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）努力削减1万亿美元的联邦支出为受虐的科技投资者增加了另一种风险，威胁要从已经不稳定的行业中获得数十亿美元的收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/musk-s-doge-spending-axe-is-hanging-over-technology-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 11:24:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普演习达成了一笔交易，而中国默默地等待舞台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2025-04-03/trump-maneuvers-for-a-tiktok-deal-while-china-waits-silently-off-stage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欢迎您深入研究Tech，这是我们的日常新闻通讯，并通过彭博新闻记者的《技术业务》的报告和分析。今天，库尔特·瓦格纳（Kurt Wagner）看着迫在眉睫的截止日期＆mdash;再次用于美国禁令或tiktok的禁令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2025-04-03/trump-maneuvers-for-a-tiktok-deal-while-china-waits-silently-off-stage</guid>
